              "Leave Payment amount blank to pay the full selected total, or type an amount if you are paying a different figure.",
              "Under Payment method, tap how you paid (for example EFT / Bank transfer).",
              "Set the Payment date. It starts on today's date.",
              "Add a Payment reference if you like, such as the EFT reference the supplier will see. This is optional.",
